  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf \u0d91\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vidda's clerk and husband remanded for the welfare of coconut workers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kaduwela Magistrate Mrs. Chamini Wijebandara today (25) ordered that a subject clerk and her husband, who were arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department for defrauding the Employees' Provident Fund of the Coconut Cultivation Board, be remanded until the 5th.",
        "R., a resident of Monaragala Okkampitiya, who is the subject clerk of the Coconut Cultivation Board, was remanded. M. Tamara Dilhani and R. D. A couple named Upul Ratnayake.",
        "Coconuts has been accused of embezzling seven crore thirty eight lakh thirty nine thousand three hundred sixty nine and thirty seven cents (Rs. 73,839,369.37) in the trust fund of the Coconut Cultivation Board established under the Coconut Development Act No. 46 of 1921 from the year 2015 to the year 2021. These suspects were arrested and brought to court by the Financial and Commercial Crime Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department in relation to a complaint made by the Development Board."
      ],
